Remarks

Class is abstract and should never be, used to annotate a class as a attribute.   Instead use a descendant, that implements the GetCaseInfoArray method.    

Note: If a method is annotated with a decendant of TestCaseSourceAttribute and returns an empty TestCaseInfoArray, then no test will be shown for the method.
